1�What's the matter with him? It's been weeks since he suddenly upped and left us in a helter-skelter.
1�And when he finally sends us a teensy-weensy message, it just reads, ??I have a lot of luggage, so come meet me at the airship port!??
1�Ahhh... The way things are going, I wonder whether our minister can really save Windurst...
1�I bet it's got to do with the minister again. I suggest we get out of here before she asks us all sorts of questions and gets us into trouble.
1�How do you like it? Windurst is a land of peace and beauty.

1�The Manustery's Cardian workshop is in Windurst Woods. It's a teeny-weeny bit far, but hey, you should know the layout of Windurst by now.

1�The Rhinostery is more like a botanical garden than a research institute. It's by far the plainest of the five ministries.
